text: Koris Vieules (born 9 October 1970) is a French equestrian. He competed in the team eventing at the 1996 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1970 births Category:Living people Category:French male equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of France Category:Equestrians at the 1996 Summer Olympics Category:People from Brive-la-Gaillarde
